Despite the "imminent disaster", students need to study, create projects and pass their final exams.
In the state of Pennsylvania, the final exam will be held on the eve of the Apocalypse, which leaves students with no choice but to work "until the night of the end of the supposed world," Restall said.
Courses have become quite popular.
